abstract: Corinna da Fonseca-Wollheim reviews chamber-music program featuring pianist Daniil Trifonov at 92nd Street Y as part of New York Philharmonic's Rachmaninoff festival.
lead_paragraph: Daniil Trifonov plays well with others at Kaufmann Concert Hall in the New York Philharmonic’s festival devoted to the composer.

headline.main: Review: Rachmaninoff Chemistry at the 92nd Street Y
